narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Absolutely. Well, it's required, but it's also a fun class and one of the highlights of my semester

A good way to prepare you for your senior essay. A good opportunity to start thinking about what your senior essay is going to be about. A good opportunity to build camaraderie among your fellow RLST majors. Not too much time spent in class. More time spent on your own working, which I found to be really helpful. Depending on your DUS, this class could be fun and helpful (which it was for me).
It help you get your senior essay ready for writing in the spring.
